Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.56,0:00:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.52,0:00:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.31,0:00:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,attained everything this world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.32,0:00:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before\Nhis death drove people to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.03,0:00:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.82,0:00:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.91,0:00:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men head for the Grand Line\Nin pursuit of their dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.67,0:00:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly\Nentered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.52,0:00:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.13,0:00:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.95,0:00:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.08,0:01:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.70,0:01:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delirious with fever,\NI take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.47,0:01:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dusty treasure map has\Nbeen verified, it's not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.59,0:01:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.22,0:01:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,simply ride aboard\Nsomeone else's biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.60,0:01:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretend it isn't there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.30,0:01:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.82,0:01:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.33,0:01:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A coin in my pocket,\Nand do you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.59,0:02:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are, We are on the cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.98,0:02:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.69,0:02:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like they pulled through. Good timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.11,0:02:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that you were going to die alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.28,0:02:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's heartbreaking, Robin-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.93,0:02:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to see people\Nsacrificing themselves anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.67,0:02:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't think of any reason\Nfor you to be kind to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.80,0:02:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...? Why did you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.14,0:03:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Parting Builds a Man's Character!\NSanji and Chopper"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.53,0:03:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to your leg?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.05,0:03:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without that leg, you won't\Nbe able to be a pirate any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.29,0:03:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.83,0:03:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...? I didn't ask for your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.00,0:03:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't think of any reason\Nfor you to be kind to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.09,0:03:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...? Why did you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.97,0:03:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.43,0:03:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You had the same dream as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.23,0:03:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The All Blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.11,0:03:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... even your men said it doesn't exist...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.99,0:03:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it does! When the\Ntime comes, head to the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.03,0:03:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The All Blue surely exists there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.58,0:04:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you see, I can't be a pirate anymore,\Nbut this time, you can go and find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.21,0:04:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! Geezer, don't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.38,0:04:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just do as you please\Nand die as you please!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.93,0:04:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That damn geezer gave up\Nhis leg so that I could live.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.81,0:04:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.23,0:04:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.48,0:04:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't repay the damn geezer for his\Nkindness unless I risk my life for him too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.29,0:04:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dying isn't something you\Nshould do to repay kindness!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.58,0:04:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what he saved you for!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.92,0:04:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being given life and yet dying...\Nis something that a weakling would do!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.96,0:04:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then is there any other way\Nto settle this matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.04,0:05:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chore boy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.74,0:05:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chore boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.54,0:05:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.29,0:05:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha! I'm not quite done yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.16,0:05:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You made me angry.\NI won't let you die so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.55,0:05:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! That bastard Krieg brings\Nout weapons one after another...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.47,0:05:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that chore boy can...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.52,0:05:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if hundreds of weapons are built in,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.15,0:05:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he can be defeated by someone\Nwith a spear of blind determination.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.24,0:06:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Life or death...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.00,0:06:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In a pirate battle, if you fear death\Nfor even a moment, you'll fall to pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.75,0:06:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.22,0:06:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.35,0:06:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that kid doesn't have any hesitation!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.28,0:06:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a survival instinct...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.45,0:06:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or does he not fear death\Nbecause he has faith in himself...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.37,0:06:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Faith...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.75,0:06:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fleet Krieg gathered...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.55,0:07:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His hundreds of weapons and poison...\NIf they're all force...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.95,0:07:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...then that kid's spear is also force...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.73,0:07:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The spear held in his heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.61,0:07:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know an idiot who's holding back\Nthat spear for a stupid reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.25,0:07:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.92,0:07:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is gonna end it... for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.69,0:07:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.57,0:07:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Giant Gavel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.50,0:08:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Wait!\N--Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.75,0:08:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We both have foolish dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.96,0:08:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.59,0:08:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to achieve my goal, the All Blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.94,0:08:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.97,0:08:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'll come along... on your journey\Nto become "King of the Pirates"!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.47,0:08:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.81,0:08:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be the cook for your ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.94,0:08:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that okay or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.40,0:08:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay!! All right!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.03,0:08:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy for you, Big Bro Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.91,0:08:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.87,0:08:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yaay! Yaay! We got a cook!\NWe'll have good food!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.16,0:08:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's how it is, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.00,0:08:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for causing you all sorts of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.71,0:09:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha! I don't like it! I wanted to\Nkick you out from here myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.68,0:09:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you decide it so easily...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.01,0:09:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for making you resort to bad acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.98,0:09:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You knew?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.73,0:09:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could hear everything, since you're all stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.48,0:09:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.95,0:09:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is to say, you're willing to go that far\Nto kick me out, huh, you damn geezer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.80,0:09:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you always have to\Ntalk like that?! You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.79,0:09:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph! That's right, little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.04,0:09:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like kids to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.83,0:09:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a single day passed where I didn't regret\Nletting a useless one live, you damn brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.92,0:09:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha! Fine by me, you damn geezer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.05,0:09:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enjoy the rest of your life to the utmost.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.73,0:09:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! This is a nice ship.\NIs it okay for us to use it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.06,0:10:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! It's Sanji's boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.57,0:10:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.90,0:10:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to say goodbye?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.36,0:10:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.41,0:10:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.41,0:10:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't catch cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.84,0:11:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Owner Zeff!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.43,0:11:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for all the damn things\Nyou've done for me over all these years!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.14,0:11:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forget your kindness...\Nfor the rest of my life!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.84,0:11:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You asshole!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.67,0:11:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll miss you, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.67,0:11:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll miss you!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.73,0:12:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll miss you!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.36,0:12:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel sad, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.79,0:12:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.56,0:12:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Men should part without a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.90,0:12:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!! Set sail!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.91,0:12:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see you again, you damn bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.67,0:12:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you don't fear even death\Nbecause you have faith in yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.74,0:13:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you'll find the All Blue... for sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.04,0:13:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! Customers are gonna show up soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.38,0:13:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get to work already!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.03,0:13:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin has been alone all this time...\Njust like I used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.37,0:13:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been shot? We need to stop\Nthe bleeding right away or you'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.96,0:13:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can! You can!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.59,0:13:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can! You can be a great doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.63,0:13:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doct... I can't breath...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.47,0:14:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...because you have such a kind heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.93,0:14:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Robin didn't\Nhave anyone like Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.52,0:14:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, there are some strange\Ncreatures in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.98,0:14:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must really have spent your\Nwhole life disliked by everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.69,0:14:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You poor monster. Why's a loner\Nlike you trying to save this country?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.20,0:14:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.45,0:14:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Even if I don't\Nhave friends, I can still fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.00,0:14:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as Doctor's flag exists, I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.00,0:14:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You do have friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.80,0:14:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am your friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.27,0:14:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let's be pirates together! Okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.02,0:14:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.15,0:14:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it is, since it's fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.86,0:14:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you don't make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.24,0:15:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.03,0:15:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm a reindeer! I have antlers and hooves!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.83,0:15:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I even have a blue nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.38,0:15:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true... that I wanna be a pirate, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.38,0:15:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not even a human! I'm a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.47,0:15:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't become your friend! So...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.56,0:15:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I just came to say thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.40,0:15:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do appreciate you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.36,0:15:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for asking me to join you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.20,0:15:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stay here, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.29,0:15:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...one day... if you feel like it, stop by agai...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.12,0:15:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.64,0:16:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't ask people to join you\Nby telling them to "shut up."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.78,0:16:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That felt good! Hey, do it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.07,0:16:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! We're setting sail right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.95,0:16:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I thought I'd die...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.83,0:16:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Where am I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.04,0:16:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Sanji-san! You came to?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.21,0:16:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor! It wasn't just a fantasy, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.42,0:16:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your research was completed then, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.63,0:16:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or was that a lie, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.26,0:16:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it, Chopper! My research succeeded!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.16,0:16:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you lie because I'd be sad\Nif you died without saying so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.27,0:16:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Nothing is impossible for the man\Nwho raised a flag with a skull!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.98,0:17:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please say it again, Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.95,0:17:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready, young men?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.53,0:17:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yes, Ma'am!\N--Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.45,0:17:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Kureha. This dust is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.92,0:17:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Kureha! What in the world...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.17,0:17:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just shut up and watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.84,0:17:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Kureha! We shot all of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.55,0:17:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light them up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.07,0:17:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.82,0:17:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.07,0:17:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.49,0:17:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will make cherry blossoms bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.87,0:17:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once my invention is complete,\Nthis country will be saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.91,0:18:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen. This red dust isn't ordinary dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.08,0:18:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will attach to the white snow in the air
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.05,0:18:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and make vivid pink snow fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.64,0:18:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.93,0:18:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctorine...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.60,0:18:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will never shoot you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.93,0:18:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Dr. Hiriluk! I'm a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.10,0:19:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tony Tony Chopper. That's a cool name,\Nisn't it? That's what I'll call you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.65,0:19:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper, you'll be able to become\Na good doctor. I'll guarantee it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.77,0:19:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I disappear, my dream will come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.01,0:19:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had... such a good life!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.55,0:19:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.85,0:19:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, have a safe trip, my stupid son...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.65,0:19:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.36,0:19:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not alone anymore, got that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.91,0:19:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll rescue you for sure, so just wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.63,0:20:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sound of the sea train?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.10,0:20:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.38,0:20:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.01,0:20:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Straw Hat Theater"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.70,0:20:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Part 4"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.95,0:20:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Ruthless Time"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.21,0:20:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'm bored.\N--Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.21,0:20:53.13,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Moai"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.13,0:20:54.44,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Moai"\N"[Bored]"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.09,0:20:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring me some meat or I'm\Ngonna frickin' kill youse guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.40,0:21:04.11,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Don Luffione, Luffione Family"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.68,0:21:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I smoke cigars, you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.47,0:21:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cuz the air in this frickin'\Nworld stinks, that's why!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.98,0:21:04.11,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,(Dandy)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.64,0:21:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I called youse guys here today for one reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.86,0:21:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's time we made clear who's\Nboss of this town once and for all!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.94,0:21:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me, you dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.11,0:21:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way, any idiot would realize it's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.09,0:21:17.04,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Don Zorocia, Zorocia Family"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.04,0:21:19.00,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Don Sanjino, Sanjino Family"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.28,0:21:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanjino, a bonehead like you who\Ndoesn't even slick his hair back
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.95,0:21:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,isn't even qualified to be boss of this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.66,0:21:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got my reasons, okay?!\NIt's slicked back on one side, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.17,0:21:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One side?! Don't make me laugh! That's like\Nsaying you've got half a pair of balls!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.55,0:21:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What'd you say?!\N--That's the last straw! This calls for all-out war!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.34,0:21:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the hell are you starting the war?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.42,0:21:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, war it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.93,0:21:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make him eat lead, Usotooya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.60,0:21:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Imma gonna take out Zorocia.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.27,0:21:50.10,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Usotooya failed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.02,0:21:51.94,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Usotooya of the Luffione Family died in battle."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.36,0:21:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go take out Luffione while he\Ndon't have his men to protect him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.78,0:21:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna take out Luffione.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.82,0:22:01.49,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopalini failed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.70,0:22:03.66,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Chopalini of the Sanjino Family died in battle."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.91,0:22:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Know your enemy well, Namimore.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.75,0:22:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna take out Sanjino.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.56,0:22:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mamma mia!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.79,0:22:13.01,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The Sanjino Family has been taken out!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.38,0:22:16.60,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Don Sanjino of the Sanjino Family\Nascended to heaven."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.13,0:22:15.80,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, where's his safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.80,0:22:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wow! He sure was loaded!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.05,0:22:22.72,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Namimore failed!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.05,0:22:24.52,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Namimore of the Zorocia Family\Ndied from happiness."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.72,0:22:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well. She still killed Sanjino.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.73,0:22:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robita, go take out Luffione.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.61,0:22:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'm not interested.\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.73,0:22:36.36,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Zorocia has been betrayed!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.48,0:22:39.96,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Don Zorocia of the Zorocia Family\Ndied thinking, 'I never thought\Nmy ally would kill me.'"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.32,0:22:41.28,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,No! They actually shot each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.20,0:22:45.17,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Robita of the Zorocia Family died thinking,\N'It wasn't supposed to be like this.'"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.28,0:22:43.89,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Robita failed!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.00,0:22:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell yeah, I'm the boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.75,0:22:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can stuff myself with as\Nmuch meat as I want in this town!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.76,0:22:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.67,0:23:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that meat tastes\Nterrible when I eat it by myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.39,0:23:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I finally realized just now\Nwhat the most important thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.43,0:23:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel lonely... I feel lonely...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.35,0:23:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this is a dream, I wanna wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.65,0:23:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh, that was a dream.\N--Who the hell are you?! And that was a dream?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.60,0:23:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The more I wish to be with them,\Nthe more I make them suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.45,0:23:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was something I dared not wish for.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.83,0:23:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Saul...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.69,0:23:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.93,0:23:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to meet friends who will protect me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.76,0:23:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.35,0:23:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Everything Is for Her Friends!\NRobin in the Darkness!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.07,0:23:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
